Class Poly

java.lang.Object
net.pl3x.map.api.markers.Poly
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable
public class Poly extends Object implements JsonSerializable
Represents a polygon in a Polygon.

A polygon requires at least one Ring to represent the outer polygon shape. Any additional rings will be used to cut out "holes" in the outer polygon.
